    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A government or political system in which absolute power or control is exercised by a single ruler or a tightly knit group of people, often with the connotation of arbitrariness and self-interest. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
